'''Arca Company Barracks''' was the barracks belonging to [[Arca Company]], at which [[Omega Squad]] and many other [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] stayed while on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. The six [[Null-class Advanced Recon Commando|''Null''-class ARC troopers]] took it over on the return from [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]], refusing to be put into [[stasis tube]]s as no one could command them during the battle. They held it against the [[Coruscant Security Force/Legends|Coruscant Security Force]] until [[Kal Skirata]] arrived, and talked them into ending the siege; Skirata was re-enlisted in the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] and the Nulls had no disciplinary action taken against them.<ref name="Republic Commando: Triple Zero">''[[Republic Commando: Triple Zero]]''</ref> The [[Special Operations Brigade/Legends|Special Operations Brigade]] was stationed here, with [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] [[Iri Camas]] and [[Arligan Zey]] maintaining offices within.

